---
// Privacy & Trust section
---

<section class="privacy section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="privacy-content reveal">
      <div class="privacy-header">
        <div class="privacy-icon">
          <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2>Your data stays private</h2>
        <p>We built TinyAct with privacy at the core. Your habit data is yours alone.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-grid">
        <div class="privacy-card">
          <div class="privacy-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>End-to-end encryption</h3>
          <p>Photo proofs are encrypted with AES-256-GCM before they leave your device. Only you and your partners can view them.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-card">
          <div class="privacy-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
              <line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="19.07" y2="19.07"></line>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>No selling your data</h3>
          <p>We don't sell your data to advertisers or third parties. Your habits are not our product.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-card">
          <div class="privacy-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"></path>
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Minimal data collection</h3>
          <p>We only collect what's needed to make the app work. No tracking, no profiling, no hidden analytics.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-card">
          <div class="privacy-card-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M3 6h18"></path>
              <path d="M19 6v14c0 1-1 2-2 2H7c-1 0-2-1-2-2V6"></path>
              <path d="M8 6V4c0-1 1-2 2-2h4c1 0 2 1 2 2v2"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Delete anytime</h3>
          <p>Request full data deletion at any time. We remove everything, no questions asked.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .privacy {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
  }

  .privacy-content {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .privacy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .privacy-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.1), rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.05));
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .privacy-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .privacy-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 450px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .privacy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .privacy-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-8);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .privacy-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .privacy-card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.1), rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.05));
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
    color: var(--green);
  }

  .privacy-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .privacy-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .privacy-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .privacy-card {
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }
  }
</style>
